name: Alt FErosFt4 (support multi-language prompt)
description:
What is?

first, This is simple a merged new model for generate realistic photography.

but,since include AltCLIP (so amazing job), now it supports almost most languages as prompt

support English(En), Chinese(Zh), Spanish(Es), French(Fr), Russian(Ru), Japanese(Ja), Korean(Ko), Arabic(Ar) and Italian(It)

Now you can generate image by your native language prompts!

Base models:

  • f222

  • aEros

  • fp-A2ft4

  • izumi

Merge parameters

Due to the use of unet-related merge methods and many minor repair merges. so, i hard cant to record merge process...😂

What is fp-A2ft4?? Where download fp-A2ft4?

fp-A2ft4 model is focus human-anatomy and art-concept model fine-tune by myself

but...

Because I wrong config it when I was training, so I ended up with only an overtrained model...so, I don't feel the need to release it...😆

However, fp-A2ft4 is very sufficient for the improvement of human body structure and the concept of Asians, which good for merging

What next?

trying to make an alt-anime model
